[div class=p 
	"Released for the Super Famicom in 1996, 
	[em 
		"Front Mission Series: Gun Hazard
	]em
	" is the second installment of the 
	[em 
		"Front Mission
	]em
	" series. Unlike the numbered titles in the series, which are isometric tactical RPGs, 
	[em 
		"Gun Hazard
	]em
	" is a side-scrolling shooter which takes place in a completely separate universe. The game was never given an offical English release, but there is a high quality fan translation made by Aeon Genesis.
]div
